    stable 2.6.7 2.6.6 2.6.4 2.6.3 2.6.2 2.6.1
   require mhash libmcrypt zlib
  category security/encryption
 attribute console
       url $SOURCEFORGE_URL
    source mcrypt/mcrypt-$VERSION.tar.gz
  homepage http://mcrypt.sourceforge.net/
  estimate 350
      desc 'mcrypt is intended to be a replacement of the old unix crypt(1) under the GPL

mcrypt is a program for encrypting files or streams.
It is intended to be a replacement for the old UNIX crypt.
It uses well-known and well-tested algorithms like DES,
BLOWFISH, TWOFISH, ARCFOUR, CAST-128, and more in several modes (CBC, CFB, etc.).
It also has a compatibility mode with the old UNIX crypt and Solaris DES.'


build(){
./configure       \
--prefix=/usr     \
--sysconfdir=/etc \
$OPTS             &&
make              &&
prepare_install   &&
make    install
}
